``` python
import time

def heart():
    for i in range(6):
        for j in range(7):
            if (i == 0 and j % 3 != 0) or (i == 1 and j == 2) or (i == 2 and j == 1) or (i == 3 and j == 0) or (i == 3 and j == 3) or (i == 3 and j == 6) or (i == 2 and j == 5) or (i == 1 and j == 4):
                print("*", end="")
            else:
                print(" ", end="")
        print("")

heart()
time.sleep(1)
print("\n I love you!")
```

这段代码可以输出一个类似爱心的符号，并在下一行输出“ I love you!”的文字。您也可以按照自己的需求进行修改和调整。
